data.description: BEAUTIFUL HOME THAT IS ON A POND LOT! FORMAL LIVING RM & DINING RM, TWO STORY/TWO CAR GARAGE. 4 BEDROOMS, 2.5 BATHS AND A HUGE LOFT AREA, GREAT FLEX SPACE. DELUXE MASTER BATH, SMOOTH TOP RANGE/DISHWASHER, AND BUILT-IN MICROWAVE. THE HOME HAS A LIVING ROOM, DINING ROOM, SPACIOUS FAMILY ROOM, AND KITCHEN WITH BREAKFAST AREA. THREE BEDROOMS HAVE A WALK-IN CLOSET. NEW ROOF IN 2022, FRESH PAINT JUST ADDED TO THE WALLS AND CEILING, AND NEW SHUTTERS ON THE OUTSIDE. NEW CARPET THROUGHOUT THE HOME. BOTH BATHROOMS HAS UPDATED SHOWERS, TUB, AND COUNTER TOPS. 1018 FRIARTUCK IS LOCATED JUST MINUTES FROM BOEING, GOOGLE PLANT,  AND VOLVO. THIS HOME IS WALKING DISTANCE FROM SANGAREE MIDDLE SCHOOL.
